titleInfo.title: Map of Cherokee Addition to Knoxville, Tenn. 1891

mods.abstract: Map of Cherokee Addition to Knoxville, Tenn. Supplement to Knoxville Daily Tribune, Sunday, October 18, 1891. Cherokee Land Company. Officers. J.C.J. Williams, President. W.J. Chandler, Vice President. R.A. McConnell, Secretary. John Bane, Treasurer and General Manager. Includes Map of the East Tennessee, Virginia & Georgia and Queen & Crescent Railway Systems. Showing location of Knoxville, Tenn. Fred S. Cully Civil Engineer, Knoxville, Tenn. H.B. Stranahan & Co. Map Engravers & Publishers, Cleveland, Ohio.
